                "post_type": "page",
                "content_format": "blocks",
                "content": "<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Summer Cookout Plan</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join us for a relaxed neighborhood summer cookout in the park. We'll fire up the grill, share favorite side dishes, and enjoy a friendly afternoon with neighbors of all ages. Bring a chair, your appetite, and anyone you'd like to introduce to the block.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Preparation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul>\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Confirm headcount and collect dietary preferences from each household.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Shop for grill supplies, drinks, and shared pantry items the day before.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Set up tables, seating, and shade in the park one hour before guests arrive.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n</ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\">View menu</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->"
            }
        }
    ],
